TITLE = Extend Notification Tone Time Limit
DESCRIPTION = Changes default notification time limit from 5 seconds to a minute. Caution: Once the notification sound is activated, there is no way to stop the event. Ringer switch works in muting the sound. Not recommended to assign long length tones.
